    <thetext>JSONEscapeSequence is different between section 15.12.1.1 &quot;JSON Lexical Grammar&quot; and annex A.8.1 &quot;JSON Lexical Grammar&quot;. The annex allows the new \u{x...} escape sequence, but that should not be valid in JSON.

RIGHT (section 15.12.1.1)

  JSONEscapeSequence ::
    JSONEscapeCharacter
    u HexDigit HexDigit HexDigit HexDigit

WRONG (annex A.8.1)

  JSONEscapeSequence ::
    JSONEscapeCharacter
    UnicodeEscapeSequence</thetext>
